place more trust in us

50
00:03:17,880 --> 00:03:19,399
(Beauty Pavilion)
upon seeing this scene.

51
00:03:19,399 --> 00:03:20,199
Two more slots remaining.

52
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:22,880
Xu Zhaozhao has come up
with plenty of ideas lately.

53
00:03:23,320 --> 00:03:25,320
- She seems pretty smart.
- Please come in.

54
00:03:30,119 --> 00:03:33,520
(He did fall for my wit and beauty.)

55
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:37,679
(On account of your fondness for me,)

56
00:03:37,679 --> 00:03:39,479
(I'll let bygones be bygones.)

57
00:03:40,759 --> 00:03:42,000
It's just

58
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:44,160
that I think she's been acting strange

59
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:47,119
ever since she became great friends
with Bingxin.

60
00:03:50,160 --> 00:03:50,720
Master.

61
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:52,360
Has our prey taken the bait?

62
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:57,600
Wrong.

63
00:03:58,360 --> 00:03:59,800
The bait has delivered herself
to our doorsteps.

64
00:04:00,399 --> 00:04:01,119
What do you need?

65
00:04:02,320 --> 00:04:03,199
Bring them there.

66
00:04:08,199 --> 00:04:09,520
Miss, would you like
to make a makeup appointment?

67
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:13,360
Welcome.

68
00:04:13,919 --> 00:04:15,720
You may purchase
whichever product you like.

69
00:04:15,720 --> 00:04:16,959
If you need to make
a makeup appointment,

70
00:04:16,959 --> 00:04:17,920
I can do that for you as well.

71
00:04:17,920 --> 00:04:18,640
So, Miss, what do you want...

72
00:04:18,640 --> 00:04:21,079
Miss, I heard that you came up
with both the Golden Phoenix Makeup

73
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:22,880
and Queen of Flowers makeup.

74
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:25,880
I wish to ask you

75
00:04:26,320 --> 00:04:27,839
if you could

76
00:04:28,200 --> 00:04:30,880
make me look 17 again?

77
00:04:32,559 --> 00:04:33,359
Make you

78
00:04:34,079 --> 00:04:36,119
look 17 again?

79
00:04:37,399 --> 00:04:38,720
That's quite difficult.

80
00:04:39,959 --> 00:04:40,799
However,

81
00:04:42,079 --> 00:04:43,399
I can help you put on

82
00:04:43,399 --> 00:04:46,119
a trendy makeup that's suitable for you.

83
00:04:46,760 --> 00:04:48,040
You should take a look first.

84
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:48,679
Come.

85
00:04:50,119 --> 00:04:51,359
Have a seat.

86
00:04:52,559 --> 00:04:53,920
Take a look at our catalog.

87
00:04:54,359 --> 00:04:56,000
We have this, this, and this.

88
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,279
Which one do you like?

89
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:59,279
I don't want any of them.

90
00:04:59,399 --> 00:05:02,920
I just want you to make me look 17 again

91
00:05:03,320 --> 00:05:05,279
so that I could meet my old flame.

92
00:05:06,959 --> 00:05:09,760
This is the portrait I had commissioned
from an artist when I was 17.

93
00:05:10,519 --> 00:05:11,480
Miss, take a look.

94
00:05:12,119 --> 00:05:13,000
See if you can do anything about it.

95
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:40,279
Speak up.

96
00:05:40,839 --> 00:05:42,040
What do you need?

97
00:05:44,399 --> 00:05:46,600
One of the customers
had a special request.

98
00:05:46,799 --> 00:05:48,839
She requested me
to make her look 17 again

99
00:05:48,839 --> 00:05:50,399
so that she could
meet her old flame again.

100
00:05:50,440 --> 00:05:51,079
Look.

101
00:05:52,079 --> 00:05:54,920
This painting depicts her and her lover.

102
00:06:03,320 --> 00:06:06,040
It's a difficult task
considering your current level.

103
00:06:06,679 --> 00:06:07,799
The underlying principle

104
00:06:07,839 --> 00:06:09,920
is the same as Bingxin's makeup.

105
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:12,040
You have to start from
her facial structure.

106
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:19,200
But why does the man

107
00:06:19,200 --> 00:06:21,519
look so familiar?

108
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:25,799
Have you seen him before?

109
00:06:26,239 --> 00:06:26,839
I haven't.

110
00:06:26,839 --> 00:06:27,839
I'm full now.

111
00:06:28,279 --> 00:06:28,920
Lin Muxuan!

112
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:34,239
I'm curious about something.

113
00:06:34,519 --> 00:06:35,359
Say,

114
00:06:35,359 --> 00:06:37,480
not only do you possess makeup skills,
but you also know how to manage a business.

115
00:06:37,799 --> 00:06:40,600
Why are you making an amateur like me
manage your business

116
00:06:40,640 --> 00:06:41,880
