117
00:06:43,079 --> 00:06:45,720
Was it truly because you didn't want
to bother yourself with the business?

118
00:06:46,440 --> 00:06:47,480
Or did you

119
00:06:48,279 --> 00:06:49,799
open Beauty Pavilion

120
00:06:50,399 --> 00:06:52,119
