besides making a profit?

121
00:06:57,519 --> 00:06:58,160
Hey!

122
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:01,600
Am I a moneygrubber to you?

123
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:04,519
Isn't that the case?

124
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:05,640
Of course not.

125
00:07:07,320 --> 00:07:08,200
Although

126
00:07:08,799 --> 00:07:12,000
I did join hands with you
for the money initially,

127
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:15,440
I've come to understand the significance
of managing one's appearance over time.

128
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:17,200
I also wish to promote Beauty Pavilion

129
00:07:17,200 --> 00:07:18,320
so that I could help out other people

130
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:19,279
and help you...

131
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:21,519
And help you to achieve your goal.

132
00:07:22,799 --> 00:07:24,079
Managing Beauty Pavilion adequately

133
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:25,519
is your goal.

134
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:27,880
You'll be free
after achieving your goal.

135
00:07:28,239 --> 00:07:29,480
You don't need to care about the rest.

136
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:31,839
Lin Muxuan.

137
00:07:33,239 --> 00:07:34,880
You can place more trust in me.

138
00:07:35,239 --> 00:07:37,399
Since we're business partners,
we have to help each other out.

139
00:07:37,679 --> 00:07:39,000
Even if you do have other goals in mind,

140
00:07:39,519 --> 00:07:41,640
